sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as Cliente HTTP
    participant RL as RateLimiter<br/>FixedWindow: 50 req/s + queue 5
    participant Ctrl as BalanceController
    participant Svc as BalanceQueryService
    participant UoW as IUnitOfWork
    participant Repo as IBalanceRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>balance.daily_balance

    Client->>RL: GET /api/v1/balance/{date}<br/>(HTTPS/JSON)
    alt Limite excedido
        RL-->>Client: 429 Too Many Requests<br/>(com Retry-After)
    else Dentro do limite
        RL->>Ctrl: GetByDate(date)
        Ctrl->>Svc: GetByDateAsync(date)
        Svc->>UoW: BeginAsync()
        Svc->>Repo: GetByDateAsync(date)
        Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM balance.daily_balance<br/>WHERE date = @date
        Note over DB: O(1) — projeção pré-calculada
        DB-->>Repo: row
        Repo-->>Svc: DailyBalance
        Svc-->>Ctrl: BalanceResponse<br/>(totalCredits, totalDebits, balance, updatedAt)
        Ctrl-->>Client: 200 OK + JSON
    end
